Because if the priest has
been waiting for the new moon,

00:17:38.993 --> 00:17:40.260 position:33% line:83% align:start
and the moon
is what affects

00:17:40.294 --> 00:17:42.229 position:5% line:89% align:start
the Earth's gravitational force,

00:17:42.262 --> 00:17:45.365 position:19% line:83% align:start
we still gotta make it
through 36 more hours of this.

00:17:45.399 --> 00:17:48.036 position:27% line:83% align:start
Listen, Jolyne,
the priest got pretty messed up

00:17:48.068 --> 00:17:49.236 position:7% line:89% align:start
during his fight with Weather.

00:17:49.269 --> 00:17:52.439 position:27% line:83% align:start
I saw it myself.
He's got some serious wounds.

00:17:52.472 --> 00:17:54.909 position:24% line:83% align:start
This is our chance
to kill the bastard

00:17:54.943 --> 00:17:56.476 position:7% line:89% align:start
while we've got him cornered.

00:17:56.511 --> 00:17:58.880 position:10% line:83% align:start
If we just keep climbing up
this guardrail,

00:17:58.913 --> 00:18:00.715 position:30% line:83% align:start
we can make it
to the Visitor Center.

00:18:01.683 --> 00:18:03.518 position:21% line:83% align:start
The priest is headed
that way, isn't he?

00:18:04.786 --> 00:18:06.353 position:27% line:89% align:start
He is. Up north.

00:18:07.589 --> 00:18:09.289 position:19% line:89% align:start
You'll do it, Jolyne.

00:18:10.024 --> 00:18:11.158 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne grunts]

00:18:11.191 --> 00:18:13.460 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:18:15.063 --> 00:18:17.732 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah. Of course,
I've already made up my mind.

00:18:17.765 --> 00:18:18.432 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exclaims]

00:18:20.535 --> 00:18:23.671 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] Yes, that's it.
It's those eyes, Jolyne.

00:18:23.705 --> 00:18:25.873 position:7% line:83% align:start
That expression when you look
into the distance.

00:18:25.907 --> 00:18:29.544 position:7% line:83% align:start
Whenever I see you like this,
my heart is set ablaze.

00:18:29.577 --> 00:18:30.845 position:24% line:89% align:start
Emporio, let's go.

00:18:31.478 --> 00:18:32.914 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yeah, sure.

00:18:32.947 --> 00:18:34.481 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:18:38.620 --> 00:18:40.521 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
I can read your heart clearly.

00:18:40.555 --> 00:18:42.657 position:24% line:83% align:start
You're filled with
an intense determination

00:18:42.690 --> 00:18:43.591 position:21% line:89% align:start
to kill the priest,

00:18:43.625 --> 00:18:45.593 position:19% line:83% align:start
and yet, it seems that
you still yearn

00:18:45.627 --> 00:18:47.562 position:27% line:83% align:start
for your father
to come save you.

00:18:47.595 --> 00:18:50.330 position:19% line:83% align:start
But what you don't see
is that I can protect you

00:18:50.364 --> 00:18:53.001 position:21% line:83% align:start
better than Weather
or Jotaro ever could.

00:18:53.034 --> 00:18:55.469 position:27% line:83% align:start
Sooner or later,
you're going to realize

00:18:55.503 --> 00:18:56.738 position:7% line:89% align:start
that you want me to be the one

00:18:56.771 --> 00:18:59.339 position:19% line:83% align:start
holding you in my arms
when this is all over.

00:19:00.541 --> 00:19:01.776 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:19:01.809 --> 00:19:03.143 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucci] At the beginning
of everything...

00:19:03.176 --> 00:19:05.278 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
...there was gravity.

00:19:06.279 --> 00:19:08.583 position:19% line:83% align:start
Even this round Earth
of ours...

00:19:08.616 --> 00:19:10.685 position:10% line:83% align:start
...was brought into reality
with gravity.

00:19:11.919 --> 00:19:13.688 position:13% line:89% align:start
[objects scrape, clatter]

00:19:14.088 --> 00:19:14.989 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crashes]

00:19:15.023 --> 00:19:16.356 position:10% line:89% align:start
With its gravitational pull,

00:19:16.390 --> 00:19:19.226 position:19% line:83% align:start
the Earth continues to
revolve around the Sun!

00:19:19.259 --> 00:19:20.962 position:24% line:83% align:start
The question that
still remains is,

00:19:20.995 --> 00:19:22.830 position:5% line:89% align:start
where on Earth am I headed now?

00:19:22.864 --> 00:19:25.332 position:7% line:89% align:start
What is going to happen next?

00:19:25.365 --> 00:19:28.503 position:13% line:83% align:start
Within my body and spirit
lies the existence of gravity,

00:19:28.536 --> 00:19:31.105 position:16% line:83% align:start
and it shall also exist
at the end of the world!

00:19:31.139 --> 00:19:32.305 position:33% line:89% align:start
[wind howls]

00:19:32.339 --> 00:19:34.742 position:24% line:89% align:start
[woman 1 sobbing]

00:19:34.776 --> 00:19:36.376 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Somebody!
-[grunts]

00:19:36.410 --> 00:19:38.813 position:13% line:89% align:start
Help! Can someone help us?

00:19:38.846 --> 00:19:41.683 position:30% line:83% align:start
What the hell
is even going on right now?

00:19:41.716 --> 00:19:44.251 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[shrieks]
-Why is this happening to us?

00:19:44.284 --> 00:19:45.285 position:27% line:89% align:start
[woman 2 yelps]

00:19:46.154 --> 00:19:47.254 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is someone there?

00:19:47.287 --> 00:19:49.189 position:27% line:89% align:start
Anyone, help us!

00:19:49.222 --> 00:19:51.291 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[thwips]
-[women sobbing]

00:19:51.324 --> 00:19:53.493 position:30% line:89% align:start
[action music]

00:19:55.495 --> 00:19:56.196 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:19:56.864 --> 00:19:58.166 position:38% line:89% align:start
Anybody!

00:19:58.198 --> 00:20:00.267 position:24% line:83% align:start
That doesn't look
too serious to me.

00:20:00.300 --> 00:20:01.669 position:21% line:89% align:start
We can let it slide.

00:20:01.703 --> 00:20:04.271 position:16% line:83% align:start
The phone isn't working.
No signal.

00:20:04.539 --> 00:20:05.238 position:38% line:89% align:start
Why not?

00:20:06.040 --> 00:20:07.909 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Emporio] I have no idea.

00:20:07.942 --> 00:20:11.378 position:5% line:83% align:start
I guess it could be that it got
broken in the wreck somehow.

00:20:11.411 --> 00:20:14.281 position:5% line:83% align:start
Or maybe it has something to do
with the strange gravity.

00:20:14.314 --> 00:20:16.050 position:30% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

00:20:16.084 --> 00:20:18.086 position:24% line:83% align:start
Anyways, I wonder
what's going on

00:20:18.119 --> 00:20:19.419 position:7% line:89% align:start
everywhere else in the world.

00:20:19.453 --> 00:20:21.089 position:21% line:89% align:start
I mean, do you think

00:20:21.122 --> 00:20:22.824 position:16% line:83% align:start
that a rescue team will
possibly show up?

00:20:25.258 --> 00:20:27.729 position:19% line:83% align:start
Looks like we made it
to the box offices, Jolyne.

00:20:28.996 --> 00:20:31.231 position:5% line:89% align:start
And over there is our entrance.

00:20:31.264 --> 00:20:34.102 position:21% line:83% align:start
The only way to get
into the Visitor Center.

00:20:34.135 --> 00:20:37.872 position:5% line:83% align:start
Jolyne, are you sure the priest
is still in this direction?

00:20:37.905 --> 00:20:39.574 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:20:41.209 --> 00:20:44.579 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's close, yeah.
I can sense him right here.

00:20:45.646 --> 00:20:48.415 position:27% line:89% align:start
[menacing music]

00:20:48.448 --> 00:20:51.519 position:10% line:83% align:start
It almost feels like he was
just standing in this spot.

00:20:52.452 --> 00:20:54.321 position:24% line:89% align:start
[heavy footsteps]

00:21:00.762 --> 00:21:01.495 position:41% line:89% align:start
[zips]

00:21:02.329 --> 00:21:03.296 position:30% line:89% align:start
What the...?!

00:21:03.898 --> 00:21:04.632 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelps]

00:21:04.665 --> 00:21:06.200 position:38% line:89% align:start
[stomps]

00:21:06.234 --> 00:21:08.368 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[Jolyne grunts]
-[Anastasia, Emporio gasp]

00:21:08.401 --> 00:21:11.371 position:7% line:89% align:start
This damn guy... Could it be?

00:21:11.404 --> 00:21:13.674 position:13% line:89% align:start
Is it really him? But why?

00:21:13.708 --> 00:21:14.876 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia gasps]

00:21:17.545 --> 00:21:19.213 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Is it Pale Snake?

00:21:19.247 --> 00:21:22.216 position:21% line:83% align:start
N-No, it looks more
like the Green Baby!

00:21:22.250 --> 00:21:23.785 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is the priest's Stand?

00:21:23.818 --> 00:21:25.318 position:21% line:89% align:start
Is it in a new form?

00:21:25.352 --> 00:21:27.487 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey, what's going on now?

00:21:27.522 --> 00:21:28.790 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[crashes]
-[Jolyne gasps]

00:21:30.725 --> 00:21:32.794 position:27% line:89% align:start
[whirrs, howls]

00:21:32.827 --> 00:21:34.294 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[banging]
-[gasps]

00:21:34.327 --> 00:21:35.295 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shatters]

00:21:35.730 --> 00:21:36.597 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:21:37.031 --> 00:21:38.266 position:33% line:89% align:start
Jolyne, no!

00:21:38.298 --> 00:21:40.333 position:24% line:89% align:start
[blood spattering]

00:21:40.735 --> 00:21:42.503 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:21:42.537 --> 00:21:45.706 position:19% line:83% align:start
Something fucked up is
happening to my right hand!

00:21:45.740 --> 00:21:47.575 position:33% line:89% align:start
[squelches]

00:21:47.608 --> 00:21:50.178 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Stand] I've come
to eliminate you for good

00:21:50.211 --> 00:21:51.879 position:16% line:83% align:start
since you couldn't wait
two more days.

00:21:51.913 --> 00:21:52.613 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:21:55.616 --> 00:21:56.551 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne breathes heavily]

00:22:07.862 --> 00:22:09.730 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music climaxes]

